[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-single-instance"
version = "0.0.0"
description = "Ensure a single instance of your tauri app is running."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"
exclude = [ "/examples",]

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tauri = "1"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies]
zbus = "3"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48"
features = [ "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_DataExchange", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_Security", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi",]

[package]
name = "tauri-plugin-window-state"
version = "0.1.0"
description = "Save window positions and sizes and restore them when the app is reopened."
authors = [ "Tauri Programme within The Commons Conservancy",]
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1"
tauri = "1"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1"
bincode = "1.3"
bitflags = "2"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]
